headline: Network Built for iPhone 17: T-Mobile COO
summary: Srini Gopalan, T-Mobile COO, says the company has the best 5G network in America and gains revenue when customers upgrade to new phones. He tells Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on "The Close" that T-Mobile built its network for products like this, highlighting its superior 5G capabilities.

headline: Deutsche Bank says ’buy the news’ in EchoStar stock after SpaceX deal
summary: Investing.com -- Deutsche Bank raised its price target on EchoStar to $102 from $67 per share in a note on Tuesday after the company agreed to sell spectrum licenses to SpaceX in a $17 billion transaction.
